headline: Smart Banking With RCU’s New Benefits Checking
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., September 04, 2025--Redwood Credit Union’s recently launched Benefits Checking isn’t just a checking account—it’s a comprehensive protection package that offers peace of mind in moments people need it most.
